Forms for admin
Secure code to email

Registration:
    captcha, if user can not auth after 3 attempts
    add "I agree terms of use" to registration form
    reset password by sms + link
    auto auth, when activation complete

Refactoring:
    sign & unsign, instead of Sign().sign() & Sign().unsign()
    check ip & user agent, when user register new auth methods

clean_auth_trash - management command
trust browser. add to settings how many days user can use browser without auth


